  "title": "Your comfy-chic holiday outfit, illustrated",
  "content": "<div><div class=\"main-content\">\n          <div class=\"thumbnail-wrapper\">\n            <figure id=\"\" class=\"figure-featured-image\"><img width=\"640\" class=\"wp-image- post-featured-image\" src=\"\" alt=\"Your comfy chic holiday outfit, illustrated\" srcset=\"https://hellogiggles.com/150w, 200w, https://hellogiggles.com/300w, 400w, https://hellogiggles.com/600w, 640w, https://hellogiggles.com/800w, 970w, https://hellogiggles.com/1200w, 1250w, https://hellogiggles.com/1400w, 1600w, https://hellogiggles.com/1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 90vw, 640px\"></figure>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"content noskimwords\">\n            <p>It’s almost that time! The time to quietly panic and throw all the clothing you own into a massive pile\n              on your mattress&nbsp;because you’re unsure of what to wear for all the holiday parties and dinners coming\n              up, that is. If you live in most places in the Northern Hemisphere, you’re probably really cold and\n              dreading wearing anything that isn’t heavy fleece. And just the thought of wearing a dress (even with\n              tights!) is most likely making you SOB right now, and we get it.</p>\n            <div class=\"vi-video-wrapper\">\n              <div class=\"vi-video-wrapper__inner vi-stories-parent-div\">\n                <div id=\"vi-content-video\" class=\"vi-stories-top-div viUnit2\">\n                  \n                  <div id=\"vi-stories-main-container\" class=\"vi-stories-main-container vi-stories-z-index-base vi-stories-width-max-500 vi-stories-overlay-ui is-controlled vi-stories-playing-content vi-stories-overlay-ui-enable\">\n                    \n                    \n                    <div id=\"vi-stories-description-container\" class=\"vi-stories-z-index-base vi-stories-hide-while-floating\">\n                      <div id=\"vi-stories-title\">Holiday and Christmas Shopping</div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <p>Which is why we put together an illustrated guide for all your holiday party and life needs!</p>\n            \n            <p><img class=\"wp-image-4253349\" src=\"https://hellogiggles.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2016/12/21/HG-Xmas-NY-Cindy-Mangomini1.jpg\" width=\"1000\" alt=\"HG-Xmas-NY-Cindy-Mangomini1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://hellogiggles.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2016/12/21/HG-Xmas-NY-Cindy-Mangomini1.jpg?quality=82&amp;strip=all 1000w, https://hellogiggles.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2016/12/21/HG-Xmas-NY-Cindy-Mangomini1.jpg?resize=300,226&amp;quality=82&amp;strip=all 300w, https://hellogiggles.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2016/12/21/HG-Xmas-NY-Cindy-Mangomini1.jpg?resize=768,578&amp;quality=82&amp;strip=all 768w, https://hellogiggles.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2016/12/21/HG-Xmas-NY-Cindy-Mangomini1.jpg?resize=500,377&amp;quality=82&amp;strip=all 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"></p>\n            <h2>Shop the illustration here:</h2>\n            <p>1. Wrap blouse, <a href=\"https://www.net-a-porter.com/gb/en/product/821067?cm_mmc=LinkshareUK-_-Hy3bqNL2jtQ-_-Custom-_-LinkBuilder&amp;siteID=Hy3bqNL2jtQ-45LKvPnBzJ6bdz86Pf5iaw\">Net-A-Porter</a>,\n              $167</p>\n            <p>2. Feline festive socks, <a href=\"http://www.modcloth.com/shop/tights-socks/feline-festive-socks\">Modcloth</a>, $8</p>\n            <p>3. Wedgie fit jeans, <a href=\"http://www.levi.com/US/en_US/womens-jeans/p/228610003\">Levi’s</a>, $89.50\n            </p>\n            <p>4. Christmas tree mug, <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/uk/listing/479831508/christmas-tree-mug-can-be-personalised?ref=hp_rv\">Etsy</a>,\n              $8</p>\n            <p>5. Vila real leather&nbsp;mittens, <a href=\"http://www.asos.com/vila/vila-real-leather-mittens/prd/7370445?iid=7370445&amp;pubref=Hy3bqNL2jtQ&amp;utm_source=Affiliate&amp;utm_medium=LinkShare&amp;utm_content=UKNetwork.1&amp;utm_campaign=Hy3bqNL2jtQ&amp;link=10&amp;promo=236989&amp;source=linkshare&amp;MID=35718&amp;affid=2134&amp;channelref=Affiliate&amp;siteID=Hy3bqNL2jtQ-rzQkKMmtDDEpmut.iq.VNQ\">ASOS</a>,\n              $30</p>\n            <p>6. Green faux suede heels, <a href=\"http://www.gojane.com/119085.html?SIZE=10&amp;id=119085-green&amp;gclid=CKarhOi-htECFcsGKgodhqUMTg\">Go\n                Jane</a>, $29</p>\n            <p>7. Holiday earrings, <a href=\"http://www.kohls.com/product/prd-2679648/christmas-tree-snowman-snowflake-drop-earring-set.jsp?ci_mcc=ci&amp;utm_campaign=UNBRANDED%20JEWELRY&amp;utm_medium=CSE&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_product=77345519&amp;CID=shopping15&amp;gclid=COGWi42_htECFYyXvQodSNcGGg&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds&amp;dclid=CNW5ro2_htECFY9vAQod6tQDCw\">Kohl’s</a>,\n              $7</p>\n          </div>\n          \n\n          \n        </div></div>",
